                <h1>Do Background Checks Include Social Media Screening?</h1>
                <p>Yes, background checks often include a search of social media profiles. Employers may review your online presence to gauge your character, professionalism, and how you present yourself publicly. This can include posts, comments, and photos, offering insights beyond what your resume provides. Always consider your digital footprint!</p>
